
Test Case Title: App feature (Local) testing

Test Case ID: LOC-05

Description: verify that you can find local stories in your area

Preconditions
The application is installed and launched.
The user has selected the local screen.

Test Steps:
Click on the local screen.
Enter your city or zipcode
or Click use device location
verify that you can see local stories in your area.

Expected result
All news content and stories should be specific to your area.

Actual result (Japan or US zip code)
US and Japan zip codes work perfectly

Actual result (other countries)
Zip code is restricted to some country
Not all city or zip code is accepted
when "Use device location" is clicked, it does not return any error message informing 
the user of the unavailability of that feature, it only bounces back
